<br>
This little change is just that, a very little change.<br>
<br>
<br>
Things that I've been pushing....<br>
<br>
1) Perforate artery from any position.<br>
2) Garrote endurance requirement severely reduced.<br>
3) Detect hidden fixes<br>
<br>
Along with some other bugs.<br>
1) Poison/bleed anti-stealth<br>
2) Snare poison going away with a successive hit<br>
<br>
The newest idea that I have been talking about is a change to perforate artery.<br>
<br>
Make perforate artery ignore some/all armor absorb.  To increase damage on perforate will just hurt the caster classes that just seem to be targets on the frontier.  Yet, we can't seem to target tank/healer/armored classes.  Making our hidden crit avoid some of the damage absorb from armor may cause...<br>
<br>
-casters to be less of a target<br>
-increases the damage we do in RVR<br>
-gives us a shot to win a duel with some of the armored classes <br>
<br>
Just some thoughts, from what I hear they are still looking into this newest change however.  Stay tuned.<br>
<br>
